# Global operating rules (Cursor only)

This file contains Cursor IDE session rules. It is **not applicable** to Claude Code sessions.

In Claude Code sessions, the authoritative lifecycle is defined in:
`~/.claude/rules/mandatory-skill-protocol.mdc` — that file is the single source of truth for all phases 0–7.

> If you are reading this as a Claude Code agent: stop here. Refer to `mandatory-skill-protocol.mdc`.
